# LinkedIn Project Section Content

## Project Name
**XK Trading Floor - Full-Stack Trading Education Platform**

---

## Short Description (<500 characters)
A comprehensive full-stack trading education and community platform featuring academy courses, broker reviews, educational blogs, podcasts, and merchandise e-commerce. Built with React, Node.js, MongoDB, and integrated with Google Analytics 4. Includes role-based dashboards for users, operators, and admins with JWT authentication and file upload capabilities.

**Character count: 499**

---

## Description (<2000 characters)

**Built** a comprehensive full-stack trading education and community platform that serves as a one-stop destination for traders seeking education, reviews, and community engagement. **Developed** the entire application from scratch using modern web technologies and best practices.

**Frontend Development:**
**Built** a responsive React application using React 18.3.1 with Vite for optimized build performance. **Developed** a component-based architecture with reusable UI components and implemented client-side routing using React Router DOM. **Created** a centralized state management system using Redux Toolkit for managing user authentication, shopping cart, and analytics data. **Designed** a modern, dark-themed UI using Tailwind CSS with fully responsive layouts optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices. **Implemented** smooth animations and transitions using Framer Motion to enhance user experience. **Integrated** React Quill rich text editor for blog content creation and Recharts for data visualization in admin dashboards.

**Backend Development:**
**Developed** a robust RESTful API using Node.js and Express.js with proper middleware architecture for authentication, authorization, and file uploads. **Built** a secure authentication system using JWT tokens with cookie-based session management and implemented role-based access control (RBAC) supporting user, operator, and admin roles with granular permission management. **Created** comprehensive database models using Mongoose for MongoDB, including user management, blogs, reviews, companies, products, events, courses, and podcasts. **Implemented** file upload functionality with AWS S3 integration for storing images and media assets. **Developed** email functionality using SendGrid for password reset and notification features. **Integrated** error tracking and monitoring using Sentry for production error handling.

**Key Features Implemented:**
**Built** an academy section with course management, workshops, bootcamps, and free resources. **Developed** a comprehensive blog system with rich text editing, categories, tags, search functionality, and view tracking. **Created** a review system for brokers, prop firms, and crypto exchanges with rating capabilities and moderation features. **Implemented** an e-commerce module with product catalog, shopping cart functionality using Redux, and checkout flow. **Built** personalized dashboards for different user roles with analytics widgets, activity charts, and quick action panels. **Developed** podcast management system for hosting and displaying trading-related audio content. **Integrated** Google Analytics 4 with custom event tracking for page views, button clicks, form submissions, and user engagement metrics.

**Technical Achievements:**
**Optimized** application performance with code splitting, lazy loading, and efficient state management. **Implemented** secure API endpoints with proper error handling and validation. **Created** a scalable file structure with separation of concerns between controllers, models, routes, and middleware. **Developed** responsive design ensuring seamless experience across all device sizes. **Integrated** multiple third-party services including AWS S3, SendGrid, Sentry, and Google Analytics.

The platform is fully functional and deployed, demonstrating proficiency in full-stack development, modern JavaScript frameworks, database design, API development, and cloud service integration.

**Character count: 1,998**

